  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is

        -  To evaluate the efficacy of association of Erythropoetin (Neorecormon) and ATRA in
           patients with low risk myelodysplastic syndromes

        -  To evaluate the tolerance of this treatment
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
